title: ASUS MB168B+ Portable Full HD USB monitor screen Unboxing - NextGenTutorials
description:
Hi Guys! Are you often on the road but love the convenience of having a portable screen with you? Well, ASUS makes that very possible with this beautiful looking mega thin ASUS MB168B+ Full HD screen! Enjoy! 


Outro music is from a friend of mine, Synthdnb please visit his SoundCloud page, he produces awesome music!!
https://soundcloud.com/synthdnb
